entry.title: mathworks/2D-Lid-Driven-Cavity-Flow-Incompressible-Navier-Stokes-Solver
entry.summary: This repository provides MATLAB code for the lid-driven cavity flow where incompressible Navier Stokes equation is numerically solved using a simple 2nd order finite difference scheme on a staggered grid system.
